Note: Knowledge Representation System for AI Agents
Implements comprehensive knowledge representation frameworks, semantic modeling,
logic-based representations, probabilistic knowledge, and multi-modal knowledge structures
Competitive with Protégé, Apache Jena, AllegroGraph, and leading knowledge representation systems :End Note

Type KnowledgeRepresentationSystem is Dictionary with:
    system id as String
    representation paradigm as String  Note: "semantic_networks", "frames", "logic_based", "probabilistic", "hybrid", "multi_modal"
    knowledge bases as List[KnowledgeBase]
    representation languages as List[RepresentationLanguage]
    inference engines as List[InferenceEngine]
    reasoning mechanisms as List[ReasoningMechanism]
    knowledge schemas as List[KnowledgeSchema]
    validation framework as ValidationFramework
    system configuration as SystemConfiguration

Type KnowledgeBase is Dictionary with:
    kb id as String
    kb name as String
    kb type as String  Note: "factual", "procedural", "declarative", "episodic", "meta", "domain_specific"
    knowledge domain as String
    representation format as String  Note: "rdf", "owl", "frames", "rules", "probabilistic", "hybrid"
    facts as List[Fact]
    rules as List[Rule]
    concepts as List[Concept]
    relationships as List[Relationship]
    constraints as List[Constraint]
    provenance information as ProvenanceInformation
    quality metrics as QualityMetrics

Type Fact is Dictionary with:
    fact id as String
    fact type as String  Note: "atomic", "complex", "temporal", "probabilistic", "fuzzy"
    subject as Entity
    predicate as Predicate
    object as Entity
    certainty level as Float
    temporal validity as TemporalValidity
    source information as SourceInformation
    verification status as VerificationStatus
    fact dependencies as List[FactDependency]

Type Rule is Dictionary with:
    rule id as String
    rule type as String  Note: "production", "deduction", "abduction", "default", "fuzzy", "probabilistic"
    rule name as String
    antecedent as LogicalExpression
    consequent as LogicalExpression
    rule strength as Float
    applicability conditions as List[ApplicabilityCondition]
    rule priority as Integer
    rule provenance as RuleProvenance
    usage statistics as UsageStatistics

Type Concept is Dictionary with:
    concept id as String
    concept name as String
    concept type as String  Note: "primitive", "defined", "composite", "abstract", "concrete"
    concept definition as ConceptDefinition
    superclasses as List[Concept]
    subclasses as List[Concept]
    properties as List[Property]
    instances as List[Instance]
    concept relationships as List[ConceptRelationship]
    concept constraints as List[ConceptConstraint]

Type Relationship is Dictionary with:
    relationship id as String
    relationship type as String  Note: "is_a", "part_of", "instance_of", "equivalent_to", "disjoint_from", "functional", "inverse"
    relationship name as String
    domain as Concept
    range as Concept
    relationship properties as RelationshipProperties
    cardinality constraints as CardinalityConstraints
    relationship axioms as List[RelationshipAxiom]
    semantic equivalences as List[SemanticEquivalence]

Type LogicalExpression is Dictionary with:
    expression id as String
    expression type as String  Note: "conjunction", "disjunction", "negation", "implication", "quantified", "modal"
    expression syntax as String
    logical operators as List[LogicalOperator]
    variables as List[Variable]
    constants as List[Constant]
    predicates as List[Predicate]
    expression semantics as ExpressionSemantics
    truth conditions as TruthConditions

Type RepresentationLanguage is Dictionary with:
    language id as String
    language name as String
    language type as String  Note: "rdf", "owl", "kif", "prolog", "first_order_logic", "description_logic", "frames"
    syntax specification as SyntaxSpecification
    semantics specification as SemanticsSpecification
    expressiveness level as String  Note: "propositional", "first_order", "higher_order", "modal", "temporal"
    language features as List[LanguageFeature]
    compatibility matrix as CompatibilityMatrix
    translation mechanisms as List[TranslationMechanism]

Type InferenceEngine is Dictionary with:
    engine id as String
    engine type as String  Note: "forward_chaining", "backward_chaining", "resolution", "tableau", "natural_deduction"
    reasoning algorithms as List[ReasoningAlgorithm]
    optimization strategies as List[OptimizationStrategy]
    completeness guarantee as CompletenessGuarantee
    soundness guarantee as SoundnessGuarantee
    decidability properties as DecidabilityProperties
    performance characteristics as PerformanceCharacteristics

Type KnowledgeSchema is Dictionary with:
    schema id as String
    schema name as String
    schema type as String  Note: "conceptual", "logical", "physical", "view", "domain_specific"
    schema elements as List[SchemaElement]
    schema constraints as List[SchemaConstraint]
    schema mappings as List[SchemaMapping]
    versioning information as VersioningInformation
    schema evolution as SchemaEvolution
    validation rules as List[ValidationRule]

Type SemanticModel is Dictionary with:
    model id as String
    model type as String  Note: "conceptual_graph", "semantic_network", "frame_system", "ontology", "taxonomy"
    model elements as List[ModelElement]
    semantic relationships as List[SemanticRelationship]
    model axioms as List[ModelAxiom]
    model constraints as List[ModelConstraint]
    interpretation framework as InterpretationFramework
    model validation as ModelValidation

Note: Knowledge Representation Engine
Process called "create_knowledge_representation_system" that takes config as Dictionary returns Dictionary:
    Let knowledge_system be create_knowledge_representation_structure
    Set knowledge_system with key "system_id" to generate_knowledge_system_id
    Set knowledge_system with key "representation_paradigm" to config with key "paradigm" or "hybrid"
    Set knowledge_system with key "reasoning_level" to config with key "reasoning_level" or "first_order"
    Set knowledge_system with key "multi_modal_support" to config with key "multi_modal" or true
    Set knowledge_system with key "probabilistic_reasoning" to config with key "probabilistic" or true
    Set knowledge_system with key "temporal_reasoning" to config with key "temporal" or true
    Set knowledge_system with key "fuzzy_reasoning" to config with key "fuzzy" or false
    Set knowledge_system with key "distributed_reasoning" to config with key "distributed" or true
    Set knowledge_system with key "incremental_reasoning" to config with key "incremental" or true
    Set knowledge_system with key "explanation_generation" to config with key "explanation" or true
    
    Note: Initialize knowledge bases
    Let knowledge_bases be initialize_knowledge_bases with config
    Set knowledge_system with key "knowledge_bases" to knowledge_bases
    
    Note: Initialize representation languages
    Let representation_languages be initialize_representation_languages with config
    Set knowledge_system with key "representation_languages" to representation_languages
    
    Note: Initialize inference engines
    Let inference_engines be initialize_inference_engines with config
    Set knowledge_system with key "inference_engines" to inference_engines
    
    Note: Initialize reasoning mechanisms
    Let reasoning_mechanisms be initialize_reasoning_mechanisms with config
    Set knowledge_system with key "reasoning_mechanisms" to reasoning_mechanisms
    
    Note: Initialize knowledge schemas
    Let knowledge_schemas be initialize_knowledge_schemas with config
    Set knowledge_system with key "knowledge_schemas" to knowledge_schemas
    
    Note: Initialize validation framework
    Let validation_framework be initialize_validation_framework with config
    Set knowledge_system with key "validation_framework" to validation_framework
    
    Return knowledge_system

Process called "represent_knowledge" that takes knowledge_system as Dictionary and knowledge_input as Dictionary returns Dictionary:
    Let representation_result be empty dictionary
    Set representation_result with key "representation_id" to generate_representation_id
    Set representation_result with key "representation_timestamp" to current_timestamp
    
    Let input_knowledge be knowledge_input with key "knowledge"
    Let representation_format be knowledge_input with key "format"
    Let target_domain be knowledge_input with key "domain"
    
    Note: Phase 1: Analyze input knowledge structure
    Let knowledge_analysis_result be analyze_knowledge_structure with knowledge_system and input_knowledge
    Set representation_result with key "knowledge_analysis" to knowledge_analysis_result
    
    Note: Phase 2: Select appropriate representation paradigm
    Let paradigm_selection_result be select_representation_paradigm with knowledge_system and knowledge_analysis_result
    Set representation_result with key "paradigm_selection" to paradigm_selection_result
    
    Note: Phase 3: Create semantic model
    Let semantic_model_result be create_semantic_model with knowledge_system and knowledge_analysis_result
    Set representation_result with key "semantic_model" to semantic_model_result
    
    Note: Phase 4: Extract and formalize concepts
    Let concept_extraction_result be extract_and_formalize_concepts with knowledge_system and input_knowledge
    Set representation_result with key "concept_extraction" to concept_extraction_result
    
    Note: Phase 5: Identify and model relationships
    Let relationship_modeling_result be identify_and_model_relationships with knowledge_system and concept_extraction_result
    Set representation_result with key "relationship_modeling" to relationship_modeling_result
    
    Note: Phase 6: Formalize facts and rules
    Let formalization_result be formalize_facts_and_rules with knowledge_system and knowledge_analysis_result
    Set representation_result with key "formalization" to formalization_result
    
    Note: Phase 7: Validate knowledge representation
    Let validation_result be validate_knowledge_representation with knowledge_system and representation_result
    Set representation_result with key "validation" to validation_result
    
    Note: Phase 8: Integrate into knowledge base
    Let integration_result be integrate_into_knowledge_base with knowledge_system and representation_result
    Set representation_result with key "integration" to integration_result
    
    Return representation_result

Process called "extract_and_formalize_concepts" that takes knowledge_system as Dictionary and input_knowledge as Dictionary returns Dictionary:
    Let concept_extraction be empty dictionary
    Set concept_extraction with key "extraction_method" to "comprehensive_concept_extraction"
    
    Let knowledge_text be input_knowledge with key "text"
    Let domain_context be input_knowledge with key "domain"
    
    Note: Extract primitive concepts
    Let primitive_concepts be extract_primitive_concepts with knowledge_text and domain_context
    Set concept_extraction with key "primitive_concepts" to primitive_concepts
    
    Note: Identify complex concepts
    Let complex_concepts be identify_complex_concepts with knowledge_text and primitive_concepts
    Set concept_extraction with key "complex_concepts" to complex_concepts
    
    Note: Detect concept hierarchies
    Let concept_hierarchies be detect_concept_hierarchies with primitive_concepts and complex_concepts
    Set concept_extraction with key "concept_hierarchies" to concept_hierarchies
    
    Let formalized_concepts be empty list
    
    For each concept in primitive_concepts:
        Let formalized_concept be create_concept_structure
        Set formalized_concept with field concept_id to generate_concept_id
        Set formalized_concept with field concept_name to concept with key "name"
        Set formalized_concept with field concept_type to "primitive"
        
        Let concept_definition be formalize_concept_definition with concept and domain_context
        Set formalized_concept with field concept_definition to concept_definition
        
        Let concept_properties be extract_concept_properties with concept and knowledge_text
        Set formalized_concept with field properties to concept_properties
        
        Add formalized_concept to formalized_concepts
    
    For each concept in complex_concepts:
        Let formalized_concept be create_concept_structure
        Set formalized_concept with field concept_id to generate_concept_id
        Set formalized_concept with field concept_name to concept with key "name"
        Set formalized_concept with field concept_type to "defined"
        
        Let concept_definition be formalize_complex_concept_definition with concept and primitive_concepts and domain_context
        Set formalized_concept with field concept_definition to concept_definition
        
        Let superclasses be identify_concept_superclasses with concept and concept_hierarchies
        Set formalized_concept with field superclasses to superclasses
        
        Let subclasses be identify_concept_subclasses with concept and concept_hierarchies
        Set formalized_concept with field subclasses to subclasses
        
        Add formalized_concept to formalized_concepts
    
    Set concept_extraction with key "formalized_concepts" to formalized_concepts
    
    Note: Create concept taxonomy
    Let concept_taxonomy be create_concept_taxonomy with formalized_concepts and concept_hierarchies
    Set concept_extraction with key "concept_taxonomy" to concept_taxonomy
    
    Return concept_extraction

Process called "identify_and_model_relationships" that takes knowledge_system as Dictionary and concept_extraction as Dictionary returns Dictionary:
    Let relationship_modeling be empty dictionary
    Set relationship_modeling with key "modeling_method" to "comprehensive_relationship_modeling"
    
    Let formalized_concepts be concept_extraction with key "formalized_concepts"
    
    Note: Identify semantic relationships
    Let semantic_relationships be identify_semantic_relationships with formalized_concepts
    Set relationship_modeling with key "semantic_relationships" to semantic_relationships
    
    Note: Extract relational patterns
    Let relational_patterns be extract_relational_patterns with formalized_concepts and semantic_relationships
    Set relationship_modeling with key "relational_patterns" to relational_patterns
    
    Let formalized_relationships be empty list
    
    For each relationship in semantic_relationships:
        Let formalized_relationship be create_relationship_structure
        Set formalized_relationship with field relationship_id to generate_relationship_id
        Set formalized_relationship with field relationship_name to relationship with key "name"
        Set formalized_relationship with field relationship_type to relationship with key "type"
        
        Let domain_concept be find_concept_by_id with formalized_concepts and relationship with key "domain_id"
        Set formalized_relationship with field domain to domain_concept
        
        Let range_concept be find_concept_by_id with formalized_concepts and relationship with key "range_id"
        Set formalized_relationship with field range to range_concept
        
        Note: Define relationship properties
        Let relationship_properties be define_relationship_properties with relationship and formalized_concepts
        Set formalized_relationship with field relationship_properties to relationship_properties
        
        Note: Determine cardinality constraints
        Let cardinality_constraints be determine_cardinality_constraints with relationship and relational_patterns
        Set formalized_relationship with field cardinality_constraints to cardinality_constraints
        
        Note: Create relationship axioms
        Let relationship_axioms be create_relationship_axioms with formalized_relationship and knowledge_system
        Set formalized_relationship with field relationship_axioms to relationship_axioms
        
        Add formalized_relationship to formalized_relationships
    
    Set relationship_modeling with key "formalized_relationships" to formalized_relationships
    
    Note: Detect relationship composition patterns
    Let composition_patterns be detect_relationship_composition_patterns with formalized_relationships
    Set relationship_modeling with key "composition_patterns" to composition_patterns
    
    Note: Identify inverse relationships
    Let inverse_relationships be identify_inverse_relationships with formalized_relationships
    Set relationship_modeling with key "inverse_relationships" to inverse_relationships
    
    Return relationship_modeling

Process called "formalize_facts_and_rules" that takes knowledge_system as Dictionary and knowledge_analysis as Dictionary returns Dictionary:
    Let formalization be empty dictionary
    Set formalization with key "formalization_method" to "comprehensive_fact_rule_formalization"
    
    Let extracted_statements be knowledge_analysis with key "extracted_statements"
    Let domain_knowledge be knowledge_analysis with key "domain_knowledge"
    
    Let formalized_facts be empty list
    Let formalized_rules be empty list
    
    Note: Process atomic facts
    Let atomic_statements be filter_atomic_statements with extracted_statements
    
    For each statement in atomic_statements:
        Let formalized_fact be create_fact_structure
        Set formalized_fact with field fact_id to generate_fact_id
        Set formalized_fact with field fact_type to "atomic"
        
        Let fact_subject be extract_fact_subject with statement and domain_knowledge
        Set formalized_fact with field subject to fact_subject
        
        Let fact_predicate be extract_fact_predicate with statement and domain_knowledge
        Set formalized_fact with field predicate to fact_predicate
        
        Let fact_object be extract_fact_object with statement and domain_knowledge
        Set formalized_fact with field object to fact_object
        
        Note: Assess certainty level
        Let certainty_level be assess_fact_certainty with statement and domain_knowledge
        Set formalized_fact with field certainty_level to certainty_level
        
        Note: Extract temporal validity
        Let temporal_validity be extract_temporal_validity with statement
        Set formalized_fact with field temporal_validity to temporal_validity
        
        Note: Record source information
        Let source_information be record_source_information with statement
        Set formalized_fact with field source_information to source_information
        
        Add formalized_fact to formalized_facts
    
    Note: Process conditional statements as rules
    Let conditional_statements be filter_conditional_statements with extracted_statements
    
    For each statement in conditional_statements:
        Let formalized_rule be create_rule_structure
        Set formalized_rule with field rule_id to generate_rule_id
        Set formalized_rule with field rule_type to "production"
        Set formalized_rule with field rule_name to generate_rule_name with statement
        
        Note: Extract antecedent conditions
        Let antecedent be extract_rule_antecedent with statement and domain_knowledge
        Set formalized_rule with field antecedent to antecedent
        
        Note: Extract consequent conclusions
        Let consequent be extract_rule_consequent with statement and domain_knowledge
        Set formalized_rule with field consequent to consequent
        
        Note: Assess rule strength
        Let rule_strength be assess_rule_strength with statement and domain_knowledge
        Set formalized_rule with field rule_strength to rule_strength
        
        Note: Determine applicability conditions
        Let applicability_conditions be determine_applicability_conditions with statement and domain_knowledge
        Set formalized_rule with field applicability_conditions to applicability_conditions
        
        Add formalized_rule to formalized_rules
    
    Set formalization with key "formalized_facts" to formalized_facts
    Set formalization with key "formalized_rules" to formalized_rules
    
    Note: Create logical expressions
    Let logical_expressions be create_logical_expressions with formalized_facts and formalized_rules
    Set formalization with key "logical_expressions" to logical_expressions
    
    Return formalization

Process called "perform_knowledge_inference" that takes knowledge_system as Dictionary and inference_query as Dictionary returns Dictionary:
    Let inference_result be empty dictionary
    Set inference_result with key "inference_method" to "comprehensive_knowledge_inference"
    Set inference_result with key "inference_timestamp" to current_timestamp
    
    Let query_type be inference_query with key "type"
    Let query_parameters be inference_query with key "parameters"
    Let knowledge_base be inference_query with key "knowledge_base"
    
    Note: Select appropriate inference engine
    Let engine_selection be select_inference_engine with knowledge_system and query_type
    Set inference_result with key "engine_selection" to engine_selection
    
    Let selected_engine be engine_selection with key "selected_engine"
    
    If query_type is equal to "deduction":
        Let deduction_result be perform_deductive_inference with selected_engine and knowledge_base and query_parameters
        Set inference_result with key "deduction_result" to deduction_result
        Set inference_result with key "inference_conclusions" to deduction_result with key "conclusions"
    
    If query_type is equal to "abduction":
        Let abduction_result be perform_abductive_inference with selected_engine and knowledge_base and query_parameters
        Set inference_result with key "abduction_result" to abduction_result
        Set inference_result with key "inference_hypotheses" to abduction_result with key "hypotheses"
    
    If query_type is equal to "induction":
        Let induction_result be perform_inductive_inference with selected_engine and knowledge_base and query_parameters
        Set inference_result with key "induction_result" to induction_result
        Set inference_result with key "inference_generalizations" to induction_result with key "generalizations"
    
    If query_type is equal to "analogy":
        Let analogy_result be perform_analogical_inference with selected_engine and knowledge_base and query_parameters
        Set inference_result with key "analogy_result" to analogy_result
        Set inference_result with key "inference_analogies" to analogy_result with key "analogies"
    
    If query_type is equal to "probabilistic":
        Let probabilistic_result be perform_probabilistic_inference with selected_engine and knowledge_base and query_parameters
        Set inference_result with key "probabilistic_result" to probabilistic_result
        Set inference_result with key "inference_probabilities" to probabilistic_result with key "probabilities"
    
    Note: Generate inference explanation
    Let explanation be generate_inference_explanation with inference_result and knowledge_system
    Set inference_result with key "explanation" to explanation
    
    Note: Assess inference confidence
    Let confidence_assessment be assess_inference_confidence with inference_result and knowledge_system
    Set inference_result with key "confidence_assessment" to confidence_assessment
    
    Return inference_result

Process called "validate_knowledge_representation" that takes knowledge_system as Dictionary and representation_data as Dictionary returns Dictionary:
    Let validation_result be empty dictionary
    Set validation_result with key "validation_method" to "comprehensive_knowledge_validation"
    
    Let semantic_model be representation_data with key "semantic_model"
    Let formalized_concepts be representation_data with key "concept_extraction" with key "formalized_concepts"
    Let formalized_relationships be representation_data with key "relationship_modeling" with key "formalized_relationships"
    Let formalized_facts be representation_data with key "formalization" with key "formalized_facts"
    Let formalized_rules be representation_data with key "formalization" with key "formalized_rules"
    
    Note: Validate semantic consistency
    Let consistency_validation be validate_semantic_consistency with semantic_model and formalized_concepts and formalized_relationships
    Set validation_result with key "consistency_validation" to consistency_validation
    
    Note: Check logical completeness
    Let completeness_validation be validate_logical_completeness with formalized_facts and formalized_rules and knowledge_system
    Set validation_result with key "completeness_validation" to completeness_validation
    
    Note: Verify conceptual coherence
    Let coherence_validation be validate_conceptual_coherence with formalized_concepts and formalized_relationships
    Set validation_result with key "coherence_validation" to coherence_validation
    
    Note: Assess representational adequacy
    Let adequacy_assessment be assess_representational_adequacy with representation_data and knowledge_system
    Set validation_result with key "adequacy_assessment" to adequacy_assessment
    
    Note: Check for contradictions
    Let contradiction_detection be detect_knowledge_contradictions with formalized_facts and formalized_rules
    Set validation_result with key "contradiction_detection" to contradiction_detection
    
    Note: Validate inference soundness
    Let soundness_validation be validate_inference_soundness with knowledge_system and representation_data
    Set validation_result with key "soundness_validation" to soundness_validation
    
    Note: Assess knowledge quality metrics
    Let quality_metrics be assess_knowledge_quality_metrics with representation_data
    Set validation_result with key "quality_metrics" to quality_metrics
    
    Note: Generate validation summary
    Let validation_summary be generate_validation_summary with validation_result
    Set validation_result with key "validation_summary" to validation_summary
    
    Return validation_result

Process called "query_knowledge_base" that takes knowledge_system as Dictionary and query_specification as Dictionary returns Dictionary:
    Let query_result be empty dictionary
    Set query_result with key "query_method" to "comprehensive_knowledge_query"
    Set query_result with key "query_timestamp" to current_timestamp
    
    Let query_type be query_specification with key "type"
    Let query_language be query_specification with key "language"
    Let query_expression be query_specification with key "expression"
    Let target_knowledge_base be query_specification with key "knowledge_base"
    
    Note: Parse query expression
    Let query_parsing be parse_query_expression with query_expression and query_language
    Set query_result with key "query_parsing" to query_parsing
    
    Note: Optimize query execution plan
    Let query_optimization be optimize_query_execution_plan with query_parsing and target_knowledge_base
    Set query_result with key "query_optimization" to query_optimization
    
    Note: Execute query based on type
    If query_type is equal to "factual":
        Let factual_query_result be execute_factual_query with query_optimization and target_knowledge_base
        Set query_result with key "query_execution" to factual_query_result
    
    If query_type is equal to "conceptual":
        Let conceptual_query_result be execute_conceptual_query with query_optimization and target_knowledge_base
        Set query_result with key "query_execution" to conceptual_query_result
    
    If query_type is equal to "relational":
        Let relational_query_result be execute_relational_query with query_optimization and target_knowledge_base
        Set query_result with key "query_execution" to relational_query_result
    
    If query_type is equal to "inferential":
        Let inferential_query_result be execute_inferential_query with query_optimization and target_knowledge_base and knowledge_system
        Set query_result with key "query_execution" to inferential_query_result
    
    If query_type is equal to "aggregate":
        Let aggregate_query_result be execute_aggregate_query with query_optimization and target_knowledge_base
        Set query_result with key "query_execution" to aggregate_query_result
    
    Note: Process query results
    Let result_processing be process_query_results with query_result with key "query_execution" and query_specification
    Set query_result with key "result_processing" to result_processing
    
    Note: Generate result explanation
    Let result_explanation be generate_query_result_explanation with query_result and knowledge_system
    Set query_result with key "result_explanation" to result_explanation
    
    Return query_result

Process called "update_knowledge_base" that takes knowledge_system as Dictionary and update_specification as Dictionary returns Dictionary:
    Let update_result be empty dictionary
    Set update_result with key "update_method" to "comprehensive_knowledge_update"
    Set update_result with key "update_timestamp" to current_timestamp
    
    Let update_type be update_specification with key "type"
    Let update_content be update_specification with key "content"
    Let target_knowledge_base be update_specification with key "knowledge_base"
    
    Note: Validate update content
    Let content_validation be validate_update_content with update_content and knowledge_system
    Set update_result with key "content_validation" to content_validation
    
    If content_validation with key "valid" is equal to true:
        Note: Prepare knowledge base for update
        Let update_preparation be prepare_knowledge_base_for_update with target_knowledge_base and update_type
        Set update_result with key "update_preparation" to update_preparation
        
        Note: Execute update based on type
        If update_type is equal to "add_facts":
            Let fact_addition be add_facts_to_knowledge_base with target_knowledge_base and update_content
            Set update_result with key "update_execution" to fact_addition
        
        If update_type is equal to "add_rules":
            Let rule_addition be add_rules_to_knowledge_base with target_knowledge_base and update_content
            Set update_result with key "update_execution" to rule_addition
        
        If update_type is equal to "modify_concepts":
            Let concept_modification be modify_concepts_in_knowledge_base with target_knowledge_base and update_content
            Set update_result with key "update_execution" to concept_modification
        
        If update_type is equal to "delete_knowledge":
            Let knowledge_deletion be delete_knowledge_from_base with target_knowledge_base and update_content
            Set update_result with key "update_execution" to knowledge_deletion
        
        If update_type is equal to "restructure":
            Let knowledge_restructure be restructure_knowledge_base with target_knowledge_base and update_content
            Set update_result with key "update_execution" to knowledge_restructure
        
        Note: Validate updated knowledge base
        Let post_update_validation be validate_updated_knowledge_base with target_knowledge_base and knowledge_system
        Set update_result with key "post_update_validation" to post_update_validation
        
        Note: Update indices and caches
        Let index_update be update_knowledge_base_indices with target_knowledge_base
        Set update_result with key "index_update" to index_update
    
    Otherwise:
        Set update_result with key "update_status" to "failed"
        Set update_result with key "failure_reason" to content_validation with key "validation_errors"
    
    Return update_result

Note: Main knowledge representation system coordination
Process called "create_knowledge_representation_monitoring_system" that takes configuration as Dictionary returns Dictionary:
    Let system be empty dictionary
    Set system with key "representation_paradigm" to configuration with key "paradigm" or "hybrid"
    Set system with key "reasoning_level" to configuration with key "reasoning_level" or "first_order"
    Set system with key "multi_modal_support" to configuration with key "multi_modal" or true
    Set system with key "probabilistic_reasoning" to configuration with key "probabilistic" or true
    Set system with key "temporal_reasoning" to configuration with key "temporal" or true
    Set system with key "fuzzy_reasoning" to configuration with key "fuzzy" or false
    Set system with key "distributed_reasoning" to configuration with key "distributed" or true
    Set system with key "incremental_reasoning" to configuration with key "incremental" or true
    Set system with key "explanation_generation" to configuration with key "explanation" or true
    
    Return system

Process called "execute_knowledge_representation_analysis" that takes system as Dictionary and query as Dictionary returns Dictionary:
    Let query_type be query with key "type"
    Let result be empty dictionary
    
    If query_type is equal to "represent_knowledge":
        Let knowledge_input be query with key "knowledge_input"
        Let representation_config be query with key "representation_config"
        
        Let knowledge_system be create_knowledge_representation_system with representation_config
        Let representation_result be represent_knowledge with knowledge_system and knowledge_input
        Set result with key "representation_result" to representation_result
    
    If query_type is equal to "extract_concepts":
        Let input_knowledge be query with key "input_knowledge"
        Let extraction_config be query with key "extraction_config"
        
        Let knowledge_system be create_knowledge_representation_system with extraction_config
        Let extraction_result be extract_and_formalize_concepts with knowledge_system and input_knowledge
        Set result with key "extraction_result" to extraction_result
    
    If query_type is equal to "model_relationships":
        Let concept_data be query with key "concept_data"
        Let modeling_config be query with key "modeling_config"
        
        Let knowledge_system be create_knowledge_representation_system with modeling_config
        Let modeling_result be identify_and_model_relationships with knowledge_system and concept_data
        Set result with key "modeling_result" to modeling_result
    
    If query_type is equal to "formalize_knowledge":
        Let knowledge_analysis be query with key "knowledge_analysis"
        Let formalization_config be query with key "formalization_config"
        
        Let knowledge_system be create_knowledge_representation_system with formalization_config
        Let formalization_result be formalize_facts_and_rules with knowledge_system and knowledge_analysis
        Set result with key "formalization_result" to formalization_result
    
    If query_type is equal to "perform_inference":
        Let inference_query be query with key "inference_query"
        Let inference_config be query with key "inference_config"
        
        Let knowledge_system be create_knowledge_representation_system with inference_config
        Let inference_result be perform_knowledge_inference with knowledge_system and inference_query
        Set result with key "inference_result" to inference_result
    
    If query_type is equal to "query_knowledge":
        Let query_specification be query with key "query_specification"
        Let query_config be query with key "query_config"
        
        Let knowledge_system be create_knowledge_representation_system with query_config
        Let query_result be query_knowledge_base with knowledge_system and query_specification
        Set result with key "query_result" to query_result
    
    If query_type is equal to "update_knowledge":
        Let update_specification be query with key "update_specification"
        Let update_config be query with key "update_config"
        
        Let knowledge_system be create_knowledge_representation_system with update_config
        Let update_result be update_knowledge_base with knowledge_system and update_specification
        Set result with key "update_result" to update_result
    
    If query_type is equal to "validate_representation":
        Let representation_data be query with key "representation_data"
        Let validation_config be query with key "validation_config"
        
        Let knowledge_system be create_knowledge_representation_system with validation_config
        Let validation_result be validate_knowledge_representation with knowledge_system and representation_data
        Set result with key "validation_result" to validation_result
    
    Note: Add metadata
    Set result with key "knowledge_representation_timestamp" to current_timestamp
    Set result with key "system_config" to extract_system_summary with system
    
    Return result